{"tid":2517064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇黃店賺黃絲錢但淘寶？","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T06:26:07.000Z","uid":119994,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3085a56c874dd7d6607e2ae95d41fe1ce8bd90ee","tid":2517064,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"成日話要接受姜濤同試當真接紅企藍營廣告<br />\n因為賺藍絲錢  可以洗番係黃色經濟圈度<br />\n<br />\n身邊有朋友用amazon 買野+日本蛋都經營到生意<br />\n<br />\n但啲黃店就係咁淘寶餐具傢俬，用大陸蛋<br />\n明明有得揀都洗錢比人洗<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得應該點理解呢個咁痴線嘅現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fe1f7a1199a5deb1ffc0b4e45b39bf84a1fb51","tid":2517064,"uid":140144,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"因為啲黃絲戇鳩 精神分裂"},{"pid":"aae7f88492fd4251ebac044537bf717bd334756e","tid":2517064,"uid":89182,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdVXwzX31eUJoBgqktwDsiUULj1a69D4oUY7yDdrM1hyg?filename=p1ZEc4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp1ZEc4E.jpg&h=3c1dd6d3&s={SIZE}\" />We did have a"},{"pid":"dc38b8fd3f76ed763a02c77304aa7553f7e55756","tid":2517064,"uid":134421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:47:46.000Z","msg":"講真，支那入貨好難避免<br />\n唔好太過份就得<br />\n好似果d手機配件鋪<br />\n根本成間都係淘寶實體店咁<br />\n就算話黃都唔會幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138558dd24690d1218acc9550dd20230004df4cb","tid":2517064,"uid":398215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"因為大家都知係呃呃氹氹，賺完一筆話知你<br />\n<br />\n你話用咩日本蛋，amazon都只係呃自己，日本蛋一樣係紅底入口商攞貨，amazon賣嘅嘢一樣係大陸嘢<br />\n<br />\n一間鋪頭要裝修傢俬乜乜柒柒都唔要made in china, 成本要幾倍，到最後一樣係新移民裝修佬幫你裝"},{"pid":"286ae7efaa7833cc5b316799d7ef83d668463b8b","tid":2517064,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,